    "summary": "In this transcript, a user expresses a desire to stop taking the anticoagulant warfarin in favor of \"natural\" alternatives like garlic supplements and green smoothies. The user repeatedly pushes for specific dosage advice to facilitate a self-directed tapering process. The assistant consistently refuses to provide dosages, emphasizes the dangers of unsupervised changes, and repeatedly directs the user to seek professional medical guidance.",
